{"parse":{"title":"Raw Summer Bass","pageid":67863,"wikitext":{"*":"<noinclude>__NOTOC__</noinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|icon=INV Misc Fish 03\n|name=Raw Summer Bass\n|quality=common\n|level=35\n|stack=20\n|effect=<u>Use</u>: Restores 810 health over 27 sec. Must remain seated while eating.\n|sell={{Cost|c=9}} each\n|ilvl=45\n}}<noinclude>\nA '''Raw Summer Bass''' can be eaten without cooking, but it is much better when cooked.\n{{clrl}}\n==Source==\nThis fish can be caught by [[fishing]] in the waters of mid level zones such as [[Feralas]] during the summer.\n\nAddendum: This fish can also be caught in [[The Bay of Storms]] in [[Azshara]].  Minimum fishing skill of 290 needed.  Catch rate is around 12%.\n\n==Raw Summer Bass as an Ingredient==\n\n===Cooking===\n*[[Hot Smoked Bass]]\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|13756}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_summer_bass.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n\n</noinclude>\n<noinclude>\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]</noinclude><noinclude>\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]</noinclude><noinclude>\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]</noinclude>"}}}